  터미널 5
  RViz 실행
source /opt/ros/jazzy/setup.bash
source ~/lidar_ws/install/setup.bash
rviz2

  RViz 설정
  Fixed Frame = map
  LaserScan Topic = /scan
  Map Topic = /map
  Update Topic = /map_updates

  터미널 6 → teleop 실행 (수동 조종)
source /opt/ros/jazzy/setup.bash
ros2 run teleop_twist_keyboard teleop_twist_keyboard


